    "extract": "AbCellera Biologics Inc. is a Vancouver, British Columbia-based biotechnology company that discovers and develops antibody therapeutics. The company is best known for its leading role in the Pandemic Prevention Platform, a project of DARPA's Biological Technologies Office. AbCellera utilizes a proprietary technology platform, which they claim can develop \"medical countermeasures within 60 days.\" Its platform for single-cell screening was initially developed at the University of British Columbia."
